Für die Begründung der Wahl, siehe Grafik S.345 Hybrid Recommender Systems: Survey and Experiments (Robin Burke)

- Used Recommendation techniques:
    - Collaborative : Identify users similar and extrapolate from their ratings of events
    - Demographic-based : Identify users that are demographically similar and extrapolate from theis ratings of events
    - Knowledge-based : Infer a match between events and the users need
    
- Hybridization method
  /* nicht sicher, welche passt
  * wird noch überarbeitet
  */
    - Weigthed: The score (votes) of several recommendation techniques are combined together to produce a single recommendation
    - Switching: The system switches between recommendation techniques depending on the current situation
    
   
